From: "Geoffrey D. Bennett" <g@b4.vu>
Date: Wed, 20 Dec 2023 04:08:42 +1030
Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: scarlett2: Add #defines for firmware upgrade
Git-commit: 103c23ccacaab14e5f8a63d60bdc4e5c81e166fc
